<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="tire-v">tire <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'taɪə(r)/    美 /'taɪər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(使) 感到累；(使) 感到厌烦：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He tired his eyes by too much reading. 
他看书太多，眼睛很累。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He tired the audience with his long speeches. 
听众对他冗长的发言感到很不耐烦。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The patient tires easily. 
病人很容易疲劳。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She <strong>never tires of</strong> talking about her children.
她总是不厌其烦地谈她的孩子。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="tire-out">tire out</h3>
<p>1.<strong>使精疲力竭</strong>  </p></div>